<subSubSection id="C32303DA8F65A77FFF3FF2493811FD27" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8650518F65A77FFF3FF2493811FD27" blockId="10.[151,1127,540,723]" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFF3FF2493D5FFDA7" bold="true" box="[151,281,572,595]" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Comments.</emphasis>
In the Palaearctic catalogue (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA82DA08F65A77FFDE3F2493F38FDA7" author="REGALIN &amp; MEDVEDEV" box="[587,894,572,595]" firstAuthor="REGALIN" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" pagination="564 - 580" refId="ref63241" refString="REGALIN R. &amp; MEDVEDEV L. N. 2010 b: Cryptocephalinae: Clytrini. Pp. 564 - 580. In: LOBL I. &amp; SMETANA A. (eds.): Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Volume 6. Chrysomeloidea. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, 924 pp." type="book chapter" year="2010" yearSuffix="b">REGALIN &amp; MEDVEDEV 2010b</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="4C392BD28F65A77FFC27F2493820FDA7" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1936" box="[911,1126,572,595]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Cyaniris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maroccana">
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFC27F2493820FDA7" box="[911,1126,572,595]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Cyaniris maroccana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is listed as a doubtful synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C392BD28F65A77FFDA8F2293FFFFD87" authority="(Lacordaire, 1848)" baseAuthorityName="Lacordaire" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[512,953,604,627]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Smaragdina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rutmana">
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFDA8F2293EAEFD87" box="[512,744,604,627]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Smaragdina ruþmana</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFA82DA08F65A77FFD5EF2293FF6FD87" author="Lacordaire" box="[758,944,604,627]" firstAuthor="Lacordaire" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" pagination="1 - 890" refId="ref59866" refString="LACORDAIRE J. T. 1848: Monographie des coleopteres subpentameres de la famille des phytophages. Tome second. Memoires de la Societe Royale des Sciences de Liege 5: i-vi + 1 - 890." type="book chapter" year="1848">Lacordaire, 1848</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Examination of the 
<typeStatus id="5482EEF38F65A77FFF16F2093CAAFD67" box="[190,236,636,659]" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">type</typeStatus>
specimen proved that 
<taxonomicName id="4C392BD28F65A77FFE71F2093EF4FD67" authorityName="Pic" authorityYear="1936" box="[473,690,636,659]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Cyaniris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maroccana">
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFE71F2093EF4FD67" box="[473,690,636,659]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Cyaniris maroccana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a valid species and belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="4C392BD28F65A77FFBA6F2093D25FD47" authority="Reitter, 1913" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1913" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chilotomina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFBA6F2093C95FD47" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Chilotomina</emphasis>
Reitter, 1913
</taxonomicName>
. Based on the original description (WARCHA 
<emphasis id="B94D8C438F65A77FFC93F2D43F01FD45" bold="true" box="[827,839,673,689]" pageId="10" pageNumber="7">Ł</emphasis>
